column2: DoubleLine Yield Opportunities Fund is a non-diversified, limited term closed-end management investment company. The Fundâ€™s investment objective is to seek a high level of total return, with an emphasis on current income. The Fund may invest indirectly by investing in derivatives or through wholly-owned and controlled subsidiaries. The Fund may be exposed to the different types of investments through its investments in a Subsidiary. Under normal market conditions, the Company seeks to achieve its investment objective by investing in a portfolio of investments selected for its potential to provide a high level of total return, with an emphasis on current income. The Fund also invests in debt securities and other income-producing investments of issuers anywhere in the world, including in emerging markets, and may invest in investments of any credit quality. DoubleLine Capital is the investment manager of the Fund.
